    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128230/extras/36e0e8e2866cd91bd8cf427e22485829.poster.avif?t=1728961028\" width=300 height=106 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128230/extras/36e0e8e2866cd91bd8cf427e22485829.webm?t=1728961028\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128230/extras/36e0e8e2866cd91bd8cf427e22485829.mp4?t=1728961028\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >解锁&amp;构筑自己的流派</h2>根据自己的战斗风格选择战士或魔法师，解锁迥然不同的技能和流派。<br>游戏还拥有超过70张职业卡牌，随着游戏进度不断解锁新卡牌，为队友提升战力的新手引导员、擅长远距离攻击和流血伤害的洗剪吹大师等等，你可以自由组建不同的流派和组合。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128230/extras/5695713cc1150a86597c08a9cc445819.poster.avif?t=1728961028\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128230/extras/5695713cc1150a86597c08a9cc445819.webm?t=1728961028\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128230/extras/5695713cc1150a86597c08a9cc445819.mp4?t=1728961028\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >充满随机乐趣的冒险</h2>游戏中有超过十几个随机事件，风浪越大鱼越贵，你敢不敢放手一搏？<br>游戏还提供了数十种魔法牌、道具牌以及武器牌，在战斗结束后商店均会随机出现，搭配你的最强牌组。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128230/extras/78de0df454ccb606a0ec0bebcc26619b.poster.avif?t=1728961028\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128230/extras/78de0df454ccb606a0ec0bebcc26619b.webm?t=1728961028\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128230/extras/78de0df454ccb606a0ec0bebcc26619b.mp4?t=1728961028\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >选择你的最佳进攻路线</h2>融合棋盘和战棋玩法，在有限的空间中玩出无限的可能，如何安排每个回合的战术将成为游戏获胜的关键！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128230/extras/2ce8504dddfb490faab357121b05cc63.poster.avif?t=1728961028\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128230/extras/2ce8504dddfb490faab357121b05cc63.webm?t=1728961028\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128230/extras/2ce8504dddfb490faab357121b05cc63.mp4?t=1728961028\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >各具特色的怪物战斗</h2>超过数十个不同特性的怪物和首领，完全不一样的技能和攻击方式。<br>优先攻击首领还是烦人的随从？什么时机哪个位置攻击才最合适？这都是你需要思考的问题！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128230/extras/8867117ae20dda124a21a4168f2d8c44.poster.avif?t=1728961028\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128230/extras/8867117ae20dda124a21a4168f2d8c44.webm?t=1728961028\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128230/extras/8867117ae20dda124a21a4168f2d8c44.mp4?t=1728961028\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>如您对游戏有任何意见和建议，欢迎进群讨论！<br>《代号肉鸽：流放之地》玩家交流群：738398261",
